The paper discusses a technique for clustering strings based on syntactic similarity and identifying patterns that describe each cluster. This technique has applications in programming-by-example workflows such as Flash Fill. Therefore, the paper is likely to belong to the Programming Languages (cs.PL), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Databases (cs.DB), Software Engineering (cs.SE), and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories.
